#. Tag: title
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:123
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kmymoney; is the Personal Finance Manager for the &kde; environment. It "
#| "provides the functions required to balance your checkbooks, manage your "
#| "personal loans and categories your incomes and expenses using a checkbook "
#| "style graphical user interface."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; is the Personal Finance Manager by &kde;. It provides the "
"functions required to balance your checkbooks, manage your personal loans "
"and categories your incomes and expenses using a checkbook style graphical "
"user interface."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; est le gestionnaire de finances personnelles de l'environnement "
"de bureau &kde;. Il fournit les fonctions nécessaires à l'équilibre de vos "
"livres de comptes, à la gestion de vos prêts personnels et de vos revenus et "
"dépenses en utilisant une interface graphique utilisateur."

